OL,3,CMan discovered by police in suitcase
OL,4,Cin woodland pictured for first time
OL,6,FA man whose body was found in a
OL,7,Fsuitcase in a Kent woodland has been
OL,8,Fpictured for the first time.
OL,10,FDale Mundell, 34, from Islington, was
OL,11,Fdiscovered by officers in Borstal last
OL,12,FFriday.
OL,14,FTwo men have since appeared in court
OL,15,Fover his death.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
