OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1784189888
OL,3,CMan discovered by police in suitcase
OL,4,Cin woodland pictured for first time
OL,6,FJoshua Miller, 32, of Kingfisher
OL,7,FCourt, Wimbledon, appeared via
OL,8,Fvideolink to Medway Magistrates' Court
OL,9,Fon Monday charged with the murder of
OL,10,FMr Mundell on July 8, and preventing a
OL,11,Flawful burial on July 9.
OL,13,FHe appeared alongside co-defendant
OL,14,FJamie Cooper, 27, of the same address,
OL,15,Fwho is charged with preventing a
OL,16,Flawful burial on July 9.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
