CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1784189888
OL,3,CMan discovered by police in suitcase
OL,4,Cin woodland pictured for first time
OL,6,FThe Metropolitan Police said officers
OL,7,Fwere called to concerns for the
OL,8,Fwelfare of a man at an address in
OL,9,FKingfisher Court, off Queensmere Road,
OL,10,FWimbledon, at around 10.55pm on July 9.
OL,12,FNobody was found at the property
OL,13,Fduring a police search, but officers
OL,14,Fbelieved someone had "come to harm" at
OL,15,Fthe address and launched an
OL,16,Finvestigation.
OL,18,FMr Mundell's family are being
OL,19,Fsupported by specialist officers.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
