FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1784189888
OL,3,CMan discovered by police in suitcase
OL,4,Cin woodland pictured for first time
OL,6,FMr Mundell and the two men charged
OL,7,Fwere known to each other, the Met
OL,8,Fadded.
OL,10,FMiller will next appear at Maidstone
OL,11,FCrown Court on Wednesday.
OL,13,FMiller and Cooper will then both
OL,14,Fappear at the same court on Monday,
OL,15,FAugust 10 for a plea hearing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/4
